text: Buildings of the Pyeongchang Olympic Village. The Pyeongchang Olympic Village is a complex of high-rise apartments in Pyeongchang County, South Korea. As an Olympic Village it hosted the attendees, which included competitors and their coaches, during the event. ==References== Category:Venues of the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Olympic Villages Category:Sports venues in Pyeongchang County Category:Buildings and structures in Pyeongchang County
title: Pyeongchang Olympic Village
